GameTooltip:SetOwner(self, "ANCHOR_TOPRIGHT"); GameTooltip:SetText("Deletes the snapshot currently selected in the dropdown menu.
This may be different from the snapshot you're currently viewing.

|c00FF0000Warning: This action cannot be undone!|r");

